# Static Methods in JavaScript Classes

```javascript
// Define a class with static method
class MathUtility {
  static add(a, b) {
    return a + b;
  }
}

// Call the static method
const sum = MathUtility.add(5, 10);
console.log(sum);
```

### Static Method Call Process:

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev
    participant MathUtility
    Dev->>MathUtility: Call add(5, 10)
